<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Créditos</title>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=10">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">  
    <htc:application
        ID="App"
        BORDER="none"
        BORDERSTYLE="normal"
        CAPTION="yes"
        SHOWINTASKBAR="yes"
        SINGLEINSTANCE="yes"
        SYSMENU="yes"
        WINDOWSTATE="normal">
    </htc:application>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .credits {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
            margin-top: -125px; /* Move o container mais para cima */
        }
        .credits h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 0.2em; /* Ajuste a margem inferior */
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .credits p {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin: 0.3em 0;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .credits p.developer {
            font-size: 1.8em; /* Tamanho intermediário da fonte */
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 1em;
            text-shadow: 0 0 1px #fff, 0 0 2px #fff, 0 0 3px #fff;
        }
        footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="credits">
        <h1>Créditos</h1>
        <p>Desenvolvido por:</p>
        <p class="developer">Memphis</p>
        <p>Obrigado por usar o meu aplicativo!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
